%% Diagram: Multiplayer Message Flow (steady state)
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant CA as Client A
    participant MP as Multiplayer<br/>(Node.js + Rust)
    participant Other as Clients B...N

    Note over CA: User edits O.P
    CA->>CA: apply optimistically,<br/>mark unacked
    CA->>MP: batched delta (~33ms)

    Note over MP: Apply in arrival order,<br/>assign seq #
    MP->>MP: update authoritative state
    MP->>MP: append to journal buffer

    par Fan-out
        MP-->>CA: ack(O, P, seq)
        MP-->>Other: broadcast(O, P, seq)
    and Durability
        MP->>MP: flush journal (~0.5s)
    end

    Note over Other: Discard if conflicts with<br/>unacked local edit on same prop
